{"id":"api/common/PercentPipe","title":"PercentPipe","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common/PercentPipe\", \"name\": \"PercentPipe\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/common/src/pipes/number_pipe.ts#L117-L182\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"percentpipe\">PercentPipe<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/PercentPipe#percentpipe\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label pipe\">pipe</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"60v0vz2v7q9vgzucpa9y590vj\">将数字转换为百分比字符串，根据确定组大小和分隔符、小数点字符和其他特定于区域设置的配置的区域设置规则进行格式化。</p>\n\n  </section>\n\n\n<section class=\"pipe-overview\">\n  <code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">{{ value_expression | <span class=\"kwd nocode\"><a href=\"api/common/PercentPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">percent</a></span> [ : digitsInfo [ : locale ] ] }}</code-example>\n\n  \n<h2 id=\"导出自\">导出自<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/PercentPipe#导出自\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\">\n      <code>CommonModule</code>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n  <h2 id=\"input-value\">输入值<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/PercentPipe#input-value\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table pipe-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6y18uxg2a2xx1qj04ok4glp0s\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>value</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string | number</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6dq37ylxcpopgzrgktoamvnbf\">要格式化为百分比的数字。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h2 id=\"parameters\">参数<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/PercentPipe#parameters\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table pipe-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"30gid03dkl55k2oxbmk61drmu\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>digitsInfo</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9fu06t45wkkjzckxe56u6wbzh\">十进制表示选项，由以下格式的字符串指定：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"94vtyn87wy2x8mdcq9mux6l3n\"><code>minIntegerDigits</code>：小数点前的最小整数位数。默认为 <code>1</code>。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9a5qzt7o2r5vj9vasyjvpufpk\"><code>minFractionDigits</code>：小数点后的最小位数。默认值为 <code>0</code>。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9m494hsapg13m9na2iwdlx9q7\"><code>maxFractionDigits</code>：小数点后的最大位数。默认值为 <code>0</code>。</li>\n</ul>\n\n        <p>可选值。默认值为 <code>undefined</code>。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"pipe-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6cuhpqqkoxc2njmr3u8ccohar\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>locale</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>string</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"afrzjhsxuuayf4aj41948q9pp\">可选值。默认值为 <code>undefined</code>。</p>\n\n        <p>可选值。默认值为 <code>undefined</code>。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">参见<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/PercentPipe#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><a href=\"api/common/formatPercent\"><code>formatPercent</code></a></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/PercentPipe#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"apxusl1k3ktgjapum5x8agd89\">以下代码显示了管道如何根据各种格式规范将数字转换为文本字符串，其中调用者的默认区域设置是 <code>en-US</code>。</p>\n<code-example path=\"common/pipes/ts/percent_pipe.ts\" region=\"PercentPipe\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'percent-pipe',\n  template: `&lt;div&gt;\n    &lt;!--output '26%'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;A: {{ a | <a href=\"api/common/PercentPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">percent</a> }}&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--output '0,134.950%'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;B: {{ b | <a href=\"api/common/PercentPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">percent</a>: '4.3-5' }}&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--output '0&nbsp;134,950 %'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;B: {{ b | <a href=\"api/common/PercentPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">percent</a>: '4.3-5' : 'fr' }}&lt;/p&gt;\n  &lt;/div&gt;`,\n})\nexport class PercentPipeComponent {\n  a: number = 0.259;\n  b: number = 1.3495;\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/CommonModule\n - api/core/PipeTransform\n - guide/ajs-quick-reference\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale\n - guide/pipes\n - guide/pipes-overview\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/CommonModule\n - api/common/PercentPipe#input-value\n - api/common/PercentPipe#parameters\n - api/common/PercentPipe#percentpipe\n - api/common/PercentPipe#see-also\n - api/common/PercentPipe#usage-notes\n - api/common/PercentPipe#导出自\n - api/common/formatPercent\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/LOCALE_ID\n - guide/i18n-common-locale-id\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/common/src/pipes/number_pipe.ts#L117-L182\n-->"}